decks.notes: The key concept of this deck is a combo strategy centered around utilizing Old Stickfingers as the commander. The deck includes cards that enable various interactions and combos, such as Buried Alive and Reanimate to quickly bring back powerful creatures from the graveyard. The inclusion of Goryo's Vengeance and Footsteps of the Goryo further supports this strategy. Additionally, the deck incorporates cards like Dark Ritual and Cabal Ritual to generate additional mana and accelerate the combo. The deck also includes disruption elements like Inquisition of Kozilek and Thoughtseize to disrupt opponents' plans. Overall, the main focus is on assembling the combo pieces and executing a powerful winning sequence.

The key concept of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures and disrupt their game plan. The deck focuses on playing low-cost artifacts and creatures to quickly build a presence on the battlefield. It utilizes cards like Steel Overseer and Chief of the Foundry to pump up its artifact creatures and gain an advantage in combat. The deck also includes disruption and removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Dispatch to deal with threats from the opponent. Additionally, cards like Winter Orb and Tangle Wire are included to slow down the opponent's mana development. The deck aims to maintain board control while applying pressure to quickly close out the game.
